data.text: They are Konstantinos Trichas and Dionysis Livanis, local artists from Greece. And this design for the cover of the Athens edition of #Designandfly with @ShowUsYourType is made by them. Discover how they got inspired here 👉 https://t.co/IpOCWVTWrD https://t.co/MseqUnGJzr

You can winter during the cold months at home ❄️ or you can take advantage to visit the Volotea cities that you have left from € 9. By the way, which one do you have left to discover?
https://t.co/oLdYl7D4lU https://t.co/E5T9ZiPc4n

If you see a heart in this picture, you need to go on a romantic getaway with your partner to Corsica and visit Les Calanques de Piana. ❤️
@ sh2808 😍
#Ajaccio #Volotea https://t.co/ghVOEDJvt4

Do not miss the small fishing village of Erbalunga a few km from Bastia. Its landscapes and its most authentic flavor will captivate you 😍
👏 @chjaracorti https://t.co/s3I7aNgnRk
Più voliamo, più vogliamo conoscere. Per questo inauguriamo 3 nuove rotte da Bari. A quale andrai prima? Prenota adesso e vola da 9€. https://t.co/Kt6MkLnFX6

Many of you have already chosen a name for your plane but, if you haven’t yet, don’t wait any longer! For sure you are TOP doing this.  You just have to go to https://t.co/q3UYhACcJ5 and tell us what name you would choose. Cross your fingers for being the most original 🤞 https://t.co/1sSoSV4EnP

Tout près de Saragosse, il y a des endroits qui vous réservent des surprises. Plus d'infos sur #VoloteaTravelBlog ! https://t.co/UgZqUFrLvV
Prenez note des lieux à ne pas manquer. https://t.co/VtG3Qiy7jG

Finally you will claim: dreams come true! Yes, because now you can get a name for a real plane ✈. You just have to go to https://t.co/u1GR5ZzIql and participate with that original, daring and fun name that you would give a plane if you had it. You can win 300 € to fly with us! https://t.co/EStOEe8arB
Più voliamo, più vogliamo conoscere. Per questo inauguriamo una nuova rotta: Palermo - Dubrovnik. Festeggia con noi e prenota i tuoi voli adesso da € 9. https://t.co/Yt8bMRVWSa

Mythology, ruins, beaches ... Let yourself be inspired by Athens, create a typographic poster of the city and participate in #DesignandFly. Check it out in this link: https://t.co/4NJszhp2FW @showusyourtype https://t.co/3XYbp56mof

data.text: Plus on vole, plus on veut en découvrir. Nous inaugurons 3 nouvelles destinations depuis Toulouse. Où irez-vous en premier ? Réservez maintenant et envolez-vous à partir de 9 €. https://t.co/36ikzuJc0D

We have made a selection of the emblematic sites of the city of Corfu and its surroundings, so that you don't miss anything on your next visit. In this #VoloteaTravelBlog you will find everything:
https://t.co/GNB0Hi8maJ https://t.co/mB0m8CqWAI
Here you have a game: do you know why Toulouse is also known as the pink city? In the photo you'll find a clue 😉 https://t.co/yIaWrxoBpL
Più voliamo, più vogliamo conoscere. Ecco perché abbiamo aperto 2 nuove rotte da Torino. Dove volerai per primo? Prenota subito e vola da € 9. https://t.co/z8zu1igbU4

The promenade of A Coruña is illuminated by 17 very artistic streetlights, decorated by the Galician artist Julia Ares with motifs related to the city. These ones, for example, are inspired by the tower of Hercules.
📷 @grupocoruna 😍 https://t.co/6oiDcH0g3X
Più voliamo, più vogliamo conoscere. Per questo inauguriamo 2 nuove rotte da Verona. Dove volerai per primo? Prenota adesso e vola da € 9. https://t.co/m2t0V4G8aW

Very close to Zaragoza there are places that will definitely surprise you. Find out more int this #VoloteaTravelBlog: https://t.co/1BrKJNeJlF
and take note of the places you shouldn't miss. https://t.co/w4Xaixbd8y
Più voliamo, più vogliamo conoscere. Ecco perché abbiamo aperto 4 nuove rotte da Venezia. Dove volerai per primo? Festeggia con noi e prenota subito i tuoi voli da € 9. https://t.co/YOQNmcZZJj
Più voliamo, più vogliamo conoscere. Ecco perché abbiamo aperto una nuova rotta: Napoli - Alicante. Festeggia con noi e prenota subito i tuoi voli da € 9. https://t.co/JuADbUNtB7
The Church of San Paolo is one of the most special places in #Olbia. Have you seen its colored dome? It certainly gives a different touch to the city skyline 🔷🔺🔶 https://t.co/UGshj851p6

Jamais on ne se lassera de le dire : Mykonos, c'est bien plus que la fête et les plages. Dans ce nouveau #VoloteaTravelBlog on a rassemblé les endroits les plus secrets qui vous seront donnés de découvrir sur l'île, comme un vrai grec !
https://t.co/k0p3w0ECbb https://t.co/v5A33i9OLE

We won't get tired of saying it: Mykonos is much more than partying and beaches. In this #VoloteaTravelBlog we have collected the most curious places for you to discover the island as a real local:
https://t.co/NBiNq3TjL5 https://t.co/KAqzY4m9F9

There are destinations that deserve to be known from the depths. In Cantabria, you can visit the @cuevaelsoplao in any of its 3 modalities: tourist, adventure and mining.
@CantabriaTurismo https://t.co/BxnHw1sTvB

What comes to mind when you think of Athens? Express it in a typographic poster and participate in #DesignandFly with @showusyourtype. The prize: € 350 and, if you are from Athens, you can also win € 300 to fly with Volotea. Conditions here: https://t.co/t97cAdCton https://t.co/hHUvmSh7re
